# tools/build/templates/

The static-site generator (`render_pages.py`) loads HTML/JSON/JSON-LD
templates from this directory. Each template is a plain text file with
`{{key}}` placeholders that the renderer substitutes with field values
from the in-memory `Catalog`.

Populated by the `ssg-per-uc-category` and `ssg-regulation-equipment`
todos. Until then this directory is intentionally empty.
